CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 20, 1957, pg. A9, reads: "Youth Lyceum Dance - The YMCA Youth Lyceum officially ended the school year with an 'End-of-School Finale,' recently. The dance was given to raise funds for the annual Youth Lyceum picnic to be held in August. Pictured are a few of the teenagers who attended the dance. Milton Swan is the youth leader. The club sponsor is Jody Harris. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Teenagers dancing in couples during YMCA Youth Lyceum "End-of-School Finale" dance
